WEBVTT

00:02.768 --> 00:04.719
[CAR HORNS HONKING]

00:08.741 --> 00:10.542
Is there anything else
I can get you?

00:12.477 --> 00:13.377
Hello?

00:15.415 --> 00:17.081
[♪♪♪]

00:17.083 --> 00:19.250
Whatever, weirdo.

00:21.000 --> 00:27.074
